      "B": "Gy (灰): 吸收劑量的 SI 單位，1 Gy = 1 J/kg。臨床通常以每日 分次 (fraction) 給予，如 2 Gy × 30 次 = 60 Gy。",
      "B_en": "Gray (Gy): SI unit of absorbed dose; 1 Gy = 1 J/kg. Clinical RT is delivered in daily fractions , e.g., 2 Gy × 30 = 60 Gy total.",
      "C": "Dose constraints 需要考慮 dose per fraction、normal tissue α/β ratio、serial vs parallel organ、prior RT history、disease-site protocol，以及 conventional fractionation vs SRS / SBRT。",
