      "D": "放射腫瘤科 (Radiation Oncology) 是使用 游離輻射 治療癌症與少數良性疾病的臨床專科。約 50% 的癌症病人在治療歷程中會接受放射治療，貢獻約 40% 的癌症治癒率。",
      "D_en": "Radiation Oncology is the medical specialty using ionizing radiation to treat cancer and select benign conditions. About 50% of cancer patients receive radiation at some point, and RT contributes ~40% of cancer cures."
