      "A_en": "Elderly or frail patients may not tolerate standard 60 Gy / 30 fractions, so treatment should be individualized. Options include 40 Gy / 15 fractions, 34 Gy / 10 fractions, 25 Gy / 5 fractions, or TMZ alone in selected MGMT promoter methylated patients with poor performance status.",
