      "C_en": "Although molecular classification is central to modern glioma diagnosis, histology remains important. Glioma grading can be remembered using \"AMEN\" or \"MEAN\": nuclear atypia, mitotic activity, endothelial or microvascular proliferation, and necrosis. More features generally indicate higher grade.",
      "D": "Brain metastases 的治療核心不是「WBRT vs SRS」二選一，而是根據 performance status、expected survival、systemic disease control、number of lesions、total intracranial tumor volume、lesion size、symptoms、LMD status 做 individualized strategy。",
      "D_en": "The core of brain metastases treatment is not a binary choice between WBRT and SRS; strategy should be individualized according to performance status, expected survival, systemic disease control, number of lesions, total intracranial tumor volume, lesion size, symptoms, and leptomeningeal disease status."
