      "exp_en": "Key point: Most locally advanced breast cancers receive neoadjuvant chemotherapy . Its goal is not simply to improve overall survival, but to downstage the tumor and nodes, increase breast-conservation feasibility, observe treatment response, and guide adjuvant escalation based on residual disease.",
      "A": "檢查評估 ：病史理學檢查、個人與家族及篩檢史、肛門指診、男性前列腺評估、女性必要時骨盆檢查、全血球計數、肝腎功能與電解質、癌胚抗原、男性 PSA、生育年齡女性懷孕檢驗、大腸鏡切片、微衛星不穩定性／錯配修復檢測、胸腹骨盆電腦斷層與直腸磁振影像。",
      "A_en": "Workup : H&P, personal/family/screening history, DRE, male prostate assessment, female pelvic exam when appropriate, CBC/CMP/CEA, PSA in men, pregnancy test in reproductive-age women, colonoscopy with biopsy, MSI/MMR testing, CT CAP, and MRI rectum with contrast.",
      "B": "局部晚期乳癌多數會接受 NAC 。NAC 的目的不是單純改善 OS，而是 downstage tumor and nodes、增加保乳可能、觀察 treatment response、並根據 residual disease 決定 adjuvant escalation。",
      "B_en": "Most locally advanced breast cancers receive neoadjuvant chemotherapy . Its goal is not simply to improve overall survival, but to downstage the tumor and nodes, increase breast-conservation feasibility, observe treatment response, and guide adjuvant escalation based on residual disease.",
      "C": "Stockholm III ：比較 25 Gy／5 次後立即手術、25 Gy／5 次後延遲手術，以及 50 Gy／25 次延遲手術且不合併同步化療。5 年局部復發 3-5%，總生存約 75%，無復發生存約 65%。短程放療後延遲手術病理完全緩解 10.4% 對立即手術 0.3%；立即手術術後併發症較多。",
      "C_en": "Stockholm III : 25 Gy/5 fx immediate surgery vs 25 Gy/5 fx delayed surgery vs 50 Gy/25 fx delayed surgery without concurrent chemo. Five-year LR 3-5%, OS about 75%, RFS about 65%. SC-RT delayed TME pCR 10.4% vs 0.3% immediate; immediate surgery had more postop complications.",
      "D": "若第二至第三期直腸癌經長程同步放化療加系統治療後達到 臨床完全緩解 ，可考慮觀察等待。此策略必須非常密集追蹤，因為局部再生長多發生在前 2 年，且需早期救援全直腸繫膜切除。",
      "D_en": "If stage II/III rectal cancer reaches clinical complete response, cCR , after LC-CRT plus systemic therapy, watch-and-wait can be considered. This strategy requires intensive follow-up because regrowth occurs mainly within the first 2 years and must be salvaged early with TME."
