      "B_en": "Workup : H&P, personal/family/screening history, DRE, male prostate assessment, female pelvic exam when appropriate, CBC/CMP/CEA, PSA in men, pregnancy test in reproductive-age women, colonoscopy with biopsy, MSI/MMR testing, CT CAP, and MRI rectum with contrast.",
      "C": "臨床重點 ：省略 RT 不是因為 RT 沒有效，而是因為在高齡、低風險、HR+、願意吃 ET 的病人中，local recurrence benefit 可能不轉化成 OS benefit。",
      "C_en": "Clinical point : radiotherapy is not omitted because it is ineffective; it is omitted because in elderly, low-risk, hormone receptor-positive patients willing to take endocrine therapy, local-recurrence benefit may not translate into overall-survival benefit.",
