      "D_en": "Most locally advanced breast cancers receive neoadjuvant chemotherapy . Its goal is not simply to improve overall survival, but to downstage the tumor and nodes, increase breast-conservation feasibility, observe treatment response, and guide adjuvant escalation based on residual disease."
