      "B_en": "STS grade is based on differentiation, mitotic count, and necrosis. Grade is central because it affects local recurrence, distant metastasis, staging, and the need for RT or systemic therapy.",
      "C": "皮膚癌最重要的危險因子是 年齡與 UV exposure 。UVB 波長約 290-320 nm，與 sunburn 和 DNA damage 關係密切；UVA 波長約 320-400 nm，與 photoaging 相關。記憶法： UVB = Burning，UVA = Aging 。",
      "C_en": "The most important skin cancer risk factors are age and UV exposure . UVB has a wavelength of about 290-320 nm and is closely linked to sunburn and DNA damage. UVA has a wavelength of about 320-400 nm and is linked to photoaging. Memory aid: UVB = Burning; UVA = Aging .",
      "D": "Aggressive T/NK-cell: Peripheral T-cell NOS、anaplastic large cell、angioimmunoblastic、extranodal NK/T nasal type、lymphoblastic lymphoma; 依組織型 systemic therapy ± RT",
      "D_en": "Aggressive T/NK-cell: Peripheral T-cell lymphoma NOS, anaplastic large cell lymphoma, angioimmunoblastic lymphoma, extranodal NK/T-cell lymphoma nasal type, lymphoblastic lymphoma; Histology-specific systemic therapy ± radiotherapy"
