      "A": "Desmoid tumor / aggressive fibromatosis: Histologically benign / non-metastatic，但 local invasion 與 recurrence 可造成 morbidity；active surveillance until progression or symptoms；systemic therapy often favored；selected progression 可 RT 56 Gy / 28 Fx",
