      "D": "Sarcoma 是一群源自 mesenchymal tissue 的異質性腫瘤，整體非常少見，約佔所有惡性腫瘤 1%。Sarcoma 有超過 100 種 histologic subtypes，約 80% 起源於 soft tissue，約 20% 起源於 bone。",
      "D_en": "Sarcoma is a heterogeneous group of malignancies arising from mesenchymal tissue . It is rare, accounting for about 1% of all malignant tumors. There are more than 100 histologic subtypes; approximately 80% arise from soft tissue and approximately 20% arise from bone."
