      "D": "MSCC: Steroids + whole-spine MRI + NSGY/RO assessment; RT alone 或 surgery + RT，依 SINS/Bilsky/NOMS; 30 Gy/10、20 Gy/5、8 Gy ×1；selected SBRT",
